product_name: Linksys AC1200 Dual Band WiFi 5 Router with Easy Setup Black
product_title: Linksys AC1200 Dual Band WiFi 5 Router with Easy Setup, Black
short_description:
Powerful, Optimized Wi-Fi Speeds
Featuring enhanced 1.2 Gbps speeds, the Linksys AC1200 Dual-Band Wi-Fi 5 Router delivers even more power, speed, range, and security for your ever-increasing networking needs. This powerful router lets you stream HD, surf, email, game, listen to music, browse, and chat, all at once. The AC1200 wireless router features dual wireless bands (2.4 GHz and 5 GHz) with data speeds up to N300 Mbps + AC867 Mbps, great for media-intense applications such as video streaming and online gaming. Beamforming focuses the Wi-Fi signal directly to your smartphones, tablets, and laptops instead of sending out a general transmission. Plus, two detachable external antennas help strengthen the signal. The result is a more efficient network with a wider range. When your device doesn't have to work as hard to receive data, it means not only greater efficiency for you, but also a longer battery life for your connected devices.
long_description:
Linksys Dual Band WiFi 5 Router

EASY SETUP: Installation is fast and easy, No CD required
DUAL-BAND WIRELESS AC: The Linksys AC1200 Dual Band WiFi 5 Router provides two dedicated Wi-Fi bands, providing double the bandwidth of a single band router.
KEEP YOUR NETWORK SAFE: Featuring WPA2 encryption and an SPI firewall, the AC1200 Dual Band WiFi 5 Router uses advanced security technologies to help keep your network safely connected.
ETHERNET FOR FAST WIRED CONNECTIONS: Four Ethernet ports allow you to connect wired devices directly for Internet access as well as share data on external storage devices.
CUSTOMIZE AND MANAGE YOUR HOME WIFI

Guest Access: Generate a separate, password-protected WiFi network for up to 10 guests and easily share the password via text.
Parental Controls: Ensure a safe Internet experience for your kids. Reduce online distractions during homework, family or dinnertime. Restrict access to inappropriate or distracting content, control usage, and block specific devices from accessing the Internet.
About Belkin International
At Belkin International, we create products that help people realize the power of technology and make people's lives better, easier and more fulfilling. This has been Belkin's mission since our inception in 1983.
Today, Belkin International has three brands – Belkin, Linksys and WeMo – to enhance the technology that connects us to the people, activities and experiences we love. Belkin products are renowned for their simplicity and ease of use, while our Linksys brand helped make wireless connectivity mainstream around the globe. Our newest brand, WeMo, is the leader in delivering customizable smart home experiences. Its product platform empowers people to monitor, measure and manage their electronics, appliances and lighting at home and on-the-go.

Join the ranks of smart home enthusiasts who have already elevated their connectivity game with the Linksys AX2200 Dual-Band Mesh WiFi 6 Router. Get yours now and enjoy a seamless, high-speed, and reliable network that will transform how you connect.

Be Home Even When You're Away

Set it to Away Mode and the Kasa Smart Plug Lite will turn connected devices on and off at different times to give the appearance that someone is home even while you're away.

Compact design makes the Kasa Smart Plug Lite considerably smaller than other smart plugs. With a thickness of just 1.5 inches, the Kasa Smart Plug Lite blends into your outlet and any room's d��cor without blocking the second outlet.

short_description:
Easy to Set Up
Step 1: Download the App by scanning QR or searching Google Play,or Scan the Qr code on the User Manual and install it.Please check if the app is up-to-date. （Android5.0 or iOS 13.0 or above）
Step 2: Plug the Smart Wi-Fi Plug into any outlet;
Step 3: Configure Smart Wi-Fi Plug preferences on the App.
Step 4: Set Your Echo Speaker by Alexa App
Step 5: Enable Our Skill in Alexa APP
Note: Please keep in mind that the App should be set up first before setting up the Alexa device,
please also refer to user manual for more detailed steps.
Note:
When the socket changed network environment, you need to restore the factory settings (Remove the socket from outlet and plug in again, press and hold on to the power button for about 5-10 seconds), and then reconnect to the network
Only support 2.4Ghz WiFi while connecting with APP. Apply to home appliances which Max load power1200W,10A, please check the load of your appliance before plugging in.
Once connected, you can use your phone via 4G or 5G Wi-Fi to turn on/off the smart plug anywhere, Please keep the smart plug stay on 2.4G Wi-Fi range always.
Tips for Quick Connection:
If the indictor doesn't flash when you plug in the smart plug for first connection, please hold a 5-10 seconds press on the button of your smart plug and see if it's start flashing.
If the smart device can't be connected to Wi-Fi, please long press On/Off button for 5~10 seconds to reset the smart plug or change the Easy mode to AP mode which is more compatible.
The smart socket only works with 2.4 Ghz network. If your router broadcasts both 2.4 and 5 Ghz, please selected the 2.4 Ghz network with the app. 
Please try to make your smart outlet and router as close as possible when first connection, you can change the place after connecting successfully.
Technical Specifications
WiFi Requirement: 2.4Ghz Only
Rated Voltage: 120V
Rated Current: 10A Max
Ac Frequency: 2.4 Ghz
Max power: 1200W
Note: The maximum power changed as the local voltage.

The smart socket only works with 2.4 Ghz network. If your router broadcasts both 2.4 and 5 Ghz, please selected the 2.4 Ghz network with the app.

short_description:
Frequently Asked Question


1. Q: Smart Plug cannot connect to Smart Life APP?

A: Check if the connected WiFi is 2.4GHz. If your router broadcasts 2.4GHz and 5GHz network, please completely turn off the 5GHz network by going to your router settings. The device amount connected to the router shouldn’t exceed its load. Try to keep your plug close to your phone and router as far as possible.

2. Q: The MAC address filtering is opened on your router. How to find the MAC address of your device?

A: Turn off the MAC address filtering, connect your device to Smart Life APP. You can find the MAC address in the Device Information after successful connection.

3. Q: The device cannot connect to Wifi after a period of use. How to reset?

A: Long press ON/OFF button for 5-10s to reset the plug or change Easy Mode to AP Mode which is more compatible.

4. Q: Cannot sync with Alexa?

A: Check if the bound Smart Life Account on Alexa APP is the same as the Smart Life APP’s. Make sure the network connection of Alexa works normally.


5. Q: Device response delay?

A: Check if the network signal is normal without delay or if the connection between the device and the router is normal. (check Device Information on Smart Life APP-whether signal strength is weak)

short_description: FAQ: Q: How to quickly switch the HomeKit and distribution modes of smart plugs? A:Long press for about 5 seconds, the led will slow blink (once per second), after 5 seconds the hotspot named Homekit_XXX will appear, so you add the plug in Home APP. Long press for about 5 seconds, the led will fast blink (twice per second), after 5 seconds, the hotpot named _XXX will appear, so you can add the plug in APP.Q: How to reset the plug to the default factory mode? A: Long press the button of the smart plug over 5s and the indicator light will blink slowly.Q: During the network configuration, is there something you should pay attention ?A: 1.Please make sure that the device, your phone and the router are close each other during the network configuration. 2.Please ensure that you key the correct password of the router. 3.During the configuration of network, please keep that the router works in the 2.4G frequency band, enables the broadcasting function and works in the non-"11n only mode". 4.During the configuration of network, please ensure that wireless encryption mode of the router is wpa2-psk and the type of authorization is AES. Or both are set to the automatic mode. 5.During the network configuration, if the router opens the wireless MAC address filter, please move the device away from the MAC filter list of the router. Please confirm whether the router has the firewall function. If this function exists, please turn off the firewall function and then try to connect the device to the router. 6.If it is a dual-frequency router, please set different passwords for 2.4G signal and 5G signal or turn off 5G signal. Please remember not opening the function of dual-frequency combination.

please also refer to user manual for more detailed steps.
Note:
When the socket changed network environment, you need to restore the factory settings (Remove the socket from outlet and plug in again, press and hold on to the power button for about 5-10 seconds), and then reconnect to the network
Only support 2.4Ghz WiFi while connecting with APP. Apply to home appliances which Max load power1200W,10A, please check the load of your appliance before plugging in.
Once connected, you can use your phone via 4G or 5G Wi-Fi to turn on/off the smart plug anywhere, Please keep the smart plug stay on 2.4G Wi-Fi range always.
Tips for Quick Connection:
If the indictor doesn't flash when you plug in the smart plug for first connection, please hold a 5-10 seconds press on the button of your smart plug and see if it's start flashing.
If the smart device can't be connected to Wi-Fi, please long press On/Off button for 5~10 seconds to reset the smart plug or change the Easy mode to AP mode which is more compatible.
The smart socket only works with 2.4 Ghz network. If your router broadcasts both 2.4 and 5 Ghz, please selected the 2.4 Ghz network with the app.
Please try to make your smart outlet and router as close as possible when first connection, you can change the place after connecting successfully.

product_name: D Link DSP W320 Outdoor Wi Fi Smart Plug
product_title: D-Link DSP-W320 Outdoor Wi-Fi Smart Plug
short_description:
Smart Home Brilliance, Made for the Outdoors

The DSP-W320 Outdoor Wi-Fi Smart Plug is a versatile and easy-to-use device that allows you to monitor and control outdoor electrical appliances from wherever you are. It has an IP54 rating, which means it can withstand outdoor weather environments such as rain, snow or dust storms. Its compact size lets you inconspicuously integrate outdoor areas into your connected home system and the legible LEDs let you know the status at a glance. Automatic scheduling provides a helpful way to save power while you're at work or asleep, and the mydlink app provides an easy way to set up alerts or manually power a device on or off, giving you peace of mind - anytime.

Weather-Resistant, Outdoor-Ready

The DSP-W320 Outdoor Wi-Fi Smart Plug is IP54 weather resistant and dust proof design keeps the Outdoor Wi-Fi Smart Plug protected in inclement weather and dusty environments. Got a sprinkler or garden hose near your power outlet? This outdoor smart plug stands up to wet encounters in your backyard, so you can be sure your connected appliances stay powered on all the time. And with weather-resistant seals, the outlets stay protected from weather penetration when not in use. Working in the garden? Well, don't worry about kicking up dust as the IP54 rating protects it from any dirt thrown at it.

Control With Your Voice

Got your hands full serving drinks or working the grill at your backyard barbecue party? The Outdoor Wi-Fi Smart Plug works with the Google Assistant and Amazon Alexa to let you turn on your fairy lights and holiday decorations instantly with voice commands. Keep your summer party guests cool with voice-activated fans, and make their jaws drop in amazement with a voice-controlled fog machine. Throwing an amazing backyard party has never been easier.

Two Independently-Controlled Outlets

Unlike other dual-outlet smart plugs that force you to turn on and off two appliances imultaneously, the Outdoor Wi-Fi Smart Plug gives you more flexibility with two independently-controlled outlets. Turn on your Christmas lights and leave the water sprinkler off. Or turn them both on if you want. It's your smart home - your choice. If you're sick and tired of connecting to and figuring out a new smart hub for every smart device in your home, you'll love the Outdoor Wi-Fi Smart Plug. It connects to your home Wi-Fi directly and easily so there's no hub required.

Get More Control With mydlink

Set up the DSP-W320 easily via the free mydlink app. Thanks to built-in Bluetooth Low Energy, you can get set up in a matter of minutes. Simply download and install the app on your mobile device and follow the step-by-step instructions to quickly configure the device.
long_description:
D-Link DSP-W320 Outdoor Wi-Fi Smart Plug
Weather-resistant (IP54) design for outdoor appliances
2 independent outlets for more flexible control over multiple devices
Smart remote power control
USB charging port
Power scheduling
Countdown timer
Automation
Wireless 802.11n - no hub required
Works with, Amazon Alexa and the Google Assistant1
Firmware over-the-air upgrade
Features: Smart Remote Control, Automation, Power Scheduling, Countdown Timer, Firmware Over-The-Air (FOTA), IEEE 802.11n/g, IEEE 802.15 BLE 4.1, IEEE 802.11 128-bit AES, System Status, Power Status, 2 x Power Button, Reset Button

short_description: Hands-Free Control via Voice CommandPower your home appliances, lamps, computers and gadgets and without lifting a finger. Say "Alexa, turn my living room fan off" as you move out of the living room. Say "Alexa, turn the bedroom lamp off" upon saying goodnight to your kids. Google Assistant grants the same hands-free convenience of the voice command feature. Just say "Google, it's time to wake up!" to get your coffee maker brewing the perfect morning coffee.Control From Anywhere Via The Free iView AppControl the iView Smart Socket from anywhere using any WiFi-enabled device. It doesn't matter if you're just in the next room, out in the garden, at work, or thousands of miles away when traveling for business or on a weekend vacation. Simply launch the iView iHome FREE app on your smartphone or tablet. Login to access your home network to remotely control your household devices anytime. As long as the appliance is on the smart plug and your cellphone is connected to the internet, you're empowered to do anything!Built-in WiFi/No Hub RequiredTransform any basic household appliance from boring to interesting! Your regular coffee maker, floor lamp and bedroom fan will instantly turn into a smart gadget by simply pairing it with the iView smart socket. Built with a 802.11 b/g/n (2.4GHz) WiFi, our smart plug eliminates the need for a hub and all the unnecessary confusion of setting it up. Not only does it skip the complicated steps, but saves you the added cost of purchasing a specialized central hub. The iView ISC300 directly connects to your router. Just enter the Wi-Fi password of your home network and you're totally in charge!Schedule and Timer FunctionSchedule your now-smart appliances, thanks to the iView WiFi socket, according to your daily routine. Create customized settings for each appliance and every family member across the different rooms of your house. Set up timers for more efficient use of appliances and energy resources. Sync your devices with your morning and bedtime regimen. Program your iView smart plug to repeat the same function as many times in a day and as needed.Single Operation or Group ControlThe iView ISC300 Wi-Fi Socket is fully integrated with Amazon Alexa, Echo, Dot and Google Home. Control connected appliances, lighting systems, and gadgets from anywhere. Manage them individually or in groups for smarter use of your home devices. Share control over home appliances and devices with family members for a personalized, more comfortable experience.Slim and Compact DesignSmart plugs, even those from well-known manufacturers, commonly arrive in big sizes. They tend to cover an entire wall socket no matter how you turn upside down and on which socket you plug it in. Some cannot be possibly rotated and can be plugged only one way. Unlike the typical rounded and bulky rectangular WiFi plugs, the iView mini smart socket does not block outlets. You can easily fit two of our space-saving smart plugs into a double socket wall outlet. Though smaller and slimmer, iView smart sockets can similarly take on a 16A load current as with popular brands. Stack em up, one at the top and one at the bottom, and make the most out of each room's power source.Energy Saver and Usage TrackerTrack energy usage around your home and find out which devices eat up the most energy. Cut power on power-hungry devices when not in use to avoid wasting energy on standby. You're certain to see results on your next energy bill. iView is committed to helping more households adapt to smart living. Our iView Wi-Fi plug offers a practical solution. Conserve energy, save on your electrical consumption, and extend the lifespan of your household appliances.

product_name: Roku Smart Home Outdoor Smart Plug SE with Custom Scheduling Independent Outlets and IP64 Weather Resistance 15 Amps
product_title: Roku Smart Home Outdoor Smart Plug SE with Custom Scheduling, Independent Outlets, and IP64 Weather Resistance - 15 Amps
short_description: Feel the power of the Roku Outdoor Smart Plug SE. You decide when your outdoor lights switch on and off with automatic scheduling you can customize right from the Roku Smart Home mobile app—you can even control them with just your voice using Alexa or a Google Assistant-enabled device. If you’re skipping town, vacation mode powers up your lights to make it look like someone’s always home. The plug even has a light sensor that can switch it on at dusk and switch it off when the sun comes up. Roku Outdoor Smart Plug SE saves money and electricity—it tracks your energy usage and sends you notifications when you’ve used more than usual. Live in the desert? Hurricane zone? No worries, Roku Outdoor Smart Plug SE is IP64 weather resistance to withstand extreme climates.
long_description:
Custom schedules: Create custom schedules for plugs to power up or down in the Roku Smart Home mobile app.
Two independent outlets: Each outlet can be controlled separately, so you can power up your holiday lights while keeping the patio lights off.
Weather resistance: IP64 weather resistance keeps your lights shining bright even during a blizzard.
Voice control Turn your plugs off or on with Alexa or a Google-Assistant enabled device.
Vacation mode: Set the plug to automatically turn on the lights and make it look like someone’s home, even when there’s not.
Smart energy tracking: Trim down your power bill with energy tracking and get alerts when you’ve exceeded a certain level.
Dusk-to-dawn light sensor: The built-in light sensor can turn the plug off when it’s light or on when it’s dark—no Wi-Fi® connection needed.
Long-range Wi-Fi® goes further: Connect to your home Wi-Fi® from up to 300 feet away.
Simple setup: Set up and plug in with one quick, guided setup in the Roku Smart Home app. No hub required.
Check device compatibility. Some devices may enter standby mode or return to default settings when turned on with Roku Outdoor Smart Plug SE. 
Requires outdoor GFCI outlet. Check outlet compatibility before purchasing Roku Outdoor Smart Plug SE.
Google and Google Home are trademarks of Google LLC. Google Assistant-enabled device required. Third party features and services may be subject to change or removal without notice.
2.4GHz Wi-Fi® required.
Features: Auto Shut-Off, Energy Efficient, Remote Controlled

product_title: Nexx WiFi Smart Plug NXPG-100W - Control, Schedule and Monitor Appliances, Lamps, and More Using Smartphone, Siri, Amazon Alexa, Google Assistant. No Hub Required, White
short_description: Nexx WiFi Smart Plug turns any regular outlet into a SMART outlet. Powered by the Nexx Home app, this smart home automation device allows you to turn on/off, monitor, and schedule all kinds of electronics - anytime, anywhere.
long_description:
MAKE ANY OUTLET SMART: Works perfectly with lamps, fans, televisions, radios, heaters, window unit air conditioners, Christmas trees, and home appliances like crock pots, curling irons, wax burners, and more.
QUICK & EASY SET-UP: Absolutely no wiring or hub required. All you need is a 2.4 GHz Wi-Fi connection. There are no hidden fees or ongoing monthly subscription! Simply plug in, connect your electronics, download the Next Home app, and go!
7 DAYS A WEEK SUPPORT!
Plug In: Nexx Smart Plug works perfectly with lamps, fans, televisions, radios, heaters, window unit air conditioners, Christmas trees, and home appliances like crock pots, curling irons, wax burners, and more. 
Power Up: Activate by tapping on the Nexx Home app or by giving voice commands to Siri or your Alexa or Google assistant-enabled devices. Or, simply drive up to your house – never come home to a dark house again!
Pick A Schedule: Make your house feel like there’s always someone home! Schedule electronics to turn on or off however you want them to, delivering extra peace of mind when you’re out of the house. Nexx Smart Plug is perfect for parents, pet owners, travelers, seniors, and people who live alone.
"Hey Siri, turn on living room lamps."  Struggling to reach the lights? Simply tell Siri to switch them on.
"Alexa, turn on Office Floor Heater."  Imagine walking into a warmer office in the middle of winter. Just tell Alexa half an hour before you head out the door.
"Hey Google, is Master Bathroom Outlet turned off?" Did you forget to turn off your curling iron? Know for sure with Nexx!
Automate Your Vacation with SmartThings! Leaving town for a week? Automate your electronics with SmartThings so that it looks like there’s always someone home!
Features: Voice Commands, Notifications, Nexx Home App, Reminders, Siri, Log, Scheduling, SmartThings, No Hub, Google Assistant, WiFi, Alexa, Sharing, Remote Controlled

product_title: Globe Electric Wi-Fi Smart Plug, No Hub Required, Voice Activated, White (1-Pack, 15A), 91005050
short_description: Automate your home with an app on your phone. It's easy. Simply download the GLOBE SUITE™ App, sync your smart device and get your home automation started. The 15-Amp Globe Electric smart plug has a compact design that allows you the convenience of having not one but three devices plugged in at the same time. Leaving one outlet free, you can use your smart plug and a smart power bar together to create a truly smart room. The plug lets you make two simple home items smart simply by plugging them in. Each outlet is independently controlled so you can automate different items at different times. Turn on your lamp from your office before you get home. Turn on your Christmas tree from your kitchen before the guests come over. Perfectly hands-free, control your plug with the sound of your voice using your Google Assistant, Amazon Alexa, or Siri. Your home, your way.
long_description:
CONTROL FROM ANYWHERE - NO HUB REQUIRED: Control all your smart devices using just your smartphone with the free GLOBE SUITE™ App. Simply download the app, connect to your home Wi-Fi, and sync your smart plug. Connect using the 2.4 GHz network connection and then go back to your 5 GHz connection if that works better for your home.
INDEPENDENTLY CONTROLLED OUTLETS: Each outlet is independently controlled so you can create a unique experience in any room of your home.
VOICE CONTROL: Using your Google Assistant, Amazon Alexa, or Siri, you can control your smart plug with just the sound of your voice making your life a whole lot easier.
SCHEDULE YOUR LIFE: Create flexible weekday and time schedules to suit your lifestyle - turn on lights when not at home, set up your nighttime routine and forget about it - make your home work for you.
SETTING THE SCENE: Using your GLOBE SUITE™ App easily create a Trigger Scene that controls many devices with one tap or create an Automatic Scene that will only activate when your set conditions are met: Turn ON Lamp 1 when it is {Sunset}.
SMART IN EVERY ROOM: The compact design is perfect for adding to every room to automate your home and make your whole house smart.
SPECIFICATIONS: System Requirements: Connect with your Wi-Fi router at 2.4 GHz; Runs on 2.4 GHz or 5 GHz after connection - Mobile device running IOS 9.0 or higher / Android 4.4 or higher; Smart Plug: 15A.

View energy reports to properly track energy usage around your home. Know which devices consume the most energy, and make plans to save energy and electricity bills.

If the power is exceeded, the power will be cut off automatically to protect the electrical appliances and maximize the lifespan.
4. Set schedule
Turn the connected device on and off at the specified time. Schedule the living room fan to turn on in the morning or schedule your child’s light to turn off to let them know it’s time to go to bed.The countdown function allows you to set a timer that automatically turns off, so you don’t have to doubt whether you have unplugged the device.
5. Voice control
Smart plugs can be used with devices supported by Alexa and Google Assistant for easy voice control.
6. No gateway required
The smart plug is suitable for any secure 2.4 GHz wireless network without the need for a separate gateway.
7. The Smart Life app is suitable for many smart home devices, allowing you to easily control your home from any Android or iOS device.
8. Applicable scenarios: living room, office, study, kitchen, bedroom, etc.

3. Open the APP and click Add socket to connect.
4. Follow the instructions on the APP to complete the operation step by step.

product_name: Smart Wall Plug YoLink 1 4 Mile World s Longest Range In Wall Outlet 15A Compatible Alexa Google Assistant IFTTT App Remote Timer Schedules Scene Aut
product_title: Smart Wall Plug, YoLink 1/4 Mile World's Longest Range Smart In-Wall Outlet 15A Compatible with Alexa Google Assistant IFTTT, App Remote Timer Schedules Scene Automation Control, YoLink Hub Required
short_description: Introducing the YoLink Smart Wall Plug: The Ultimate Solution for Smart Home Automation with the World's Longest Range of 1/4 Mile! Our innovative smart in-wall outlet is designed to work seamlessly with Alexa, Google Assistant, and IFTTT, providing you with the convenience of remote control, timer schedules, scene automation, and custom controls. With an exceptional range and unmatched performance, the YoLink Smart Wall Plug is the perfect solution for your smart home automation needs – and don't forget, the YoLink Hub is required!
long_description:
World's Longest Wireless Range: Powered by LoRa technology, the long-range yet low-power system offers the industry’s longest receiving range in the market (1/4 mile). Our long-range coverage enables its use in areas challenging for most residential Wi-Fi systems, such as basements, outdoor porch/patio areas, sheds, free-standing garages, even remote outbuildings on your property.

Works With Alexa & Google Voice Assistants: Supercharge your YoLink system by adding the YoLink skill to Alexa or Google Assistant. Control your YoLink devices by voice command (“Alexa, turn off the fan” – “OK!”) and control your YoLink devices as part of routines/automations that may include other, third-party, smart devices integrated with Alexa/Google.

Simple & Easy! YoLink’s Scan & Play smartphone app feature will have your smart plug up & ready in just a couple minutes! And the Wall Plug could not be easier to install: just add it to the app, and plug it into an available 120V receptacle. Done! Enjoy the convenience and energy bill savings of your new smart plug.

Set it & Forget it: Tired of forgetting to turn something off, or worried about leaving an iron or space heater on, or are there appliances/devices that you regularly turn off/on but wish it was automatic? Now, use the YoLink app to schedule automations, to automatically turn the power on or off at the time of your choice, on the days of the week of your choice.

YoLink Hub Required but not included: YoLink Hub is the only central controller for YoLink devices, and it connects YoLink devices into the internet and the cloud. Without YoLink Hub, YoLink smart power strip does not work with YoLink app and does not support 3rd-party integration with Alexa, Google Home and IFTTT.
The YoLink Smart Wall Plug sets the standard for smart home automation, offering an incredible 1/4 mile range that ensures reliable connectivity to your devices, no matter where you are on your property. Our innovative smart in-wall outlet is designed to handle up to 15A of power, making it the perfect solution for a wide range of devices, including lamps, fans, and small appliances.

Experience the convenience of the easy-to-use app, allowing you to customize your settings and receive real-time alerts directly to your smartphone. Seamlessly integrate the YoLink Smart Wall Plug with Alexa, Google Assistant, and IFTTT, enabling convenient voice commands and custom automations tailored to your unique needs.

Our versatile smart in-wall outlet is perfect for controlling any device you want to add to your smart home automation system, with the convenience of remote control, timer schedules, scene automation, and custom controls. Whether you're at home or away, you can always stay connected and in control.

Stay informed and in control with real-time app notifications, ensuring you're always aware of the status of your smart home devices. The YoLink Smart Wall Plug is the perfect addition to any smart home ecosystem, offering unparalleled range, versatility, and convenience.

Upgrade your smart home automation experience with the YoLink Smart Wall Plug, and discover the perfect combination of range, performance, and control. Transform your home into a fully automated smart home, and embrace the YoLink difference today!

product_title: BRAUMM WiFi Smart Plug, ETL Listed Smart WiFi Plug Remote Monitor, Outlet Timer Compatible with Alexa and Google Assistant Voice Control
short_description:
Automate Your Home with a WiFi Smart Plug
Do you like to return to a well-lit home after work? Are you tired of running all over to turn off the lights and fans before bed? The BRAUMM WiFi smart plug allows you to easily do all of the above.

Make Control Easy and Fun
The BRAUMM smart plug outlet is one of the easiest way to upgrade your home devices and turn them to smart devices. You can control all of them with your smartphone or through voice commands to Amazon Alexa or Google Assistant. You can easily add family members and grant them access to control the smart devices.

Set Schedule, Smart Scenes and Automation
Improve home security and use BRAUMM app to create schedules to automate your plug(s) when you are away from home. You can also use Smart Scene to turn on/off a group of devices for special occasions. The Automation will turn on/off the fan or lights based on the weather, temperature, etc. Also compatible with SmartLife App.

Easy Setup and Safety for You and Your Family
The WiFi smart plug is ready to pair once it’s plugged in - no additional hub required. Just download the BRAUMM app and follow the in-app instructions to pair the plug(s) with the app. The overcurrent protection cuts off power when the plug is overloaded.

Limited Lifetime Warranty
Every BRAUMM product comes with a limited lifetime warranty. Please refer to BRAUMM's website for more information.

Specifications
Power supply: AC 90 – 135V, 60Hz
Nominal input voltage: AC 120V
Standby power loss: ≤ 1W
Rated current: 10A max
Wireless frequency: 2.412 GHz – 2.484 GHz
Network Protocol: IEEE802.11 b/g/n
Encryption type: WEP/TKIP/AES, WPS
Working temperature: 14°F to 104°F / -10°C to 40°C
Storage temperature: -4°F to 140°F / -20°C to 60°C
Relative humidity: 8% - 80% RH

Package Includes
1x BRAUMM Wi-Fi Smart Plug
1x User Manual
long_description:
[INSTANTLY UPGRADE TO A SMART OUTLET] The BRAUMM WiFi smart plug can easily upgrade your standard outlet to a multifunctional smart outlet. With the BRAUMM app, you are able to automate the smart outlet any way you like. The plug ONLY supports 2.4G WiFi, and no hub is required.
[VOICE CONTROL] Link your smart plug to Alexa or Google Assistant via the BRAUMM Control Alexa Skill or Google Action. Name your device whatever you want, and enjoy the convenience of Alexa or Google Assistant. Say “Alexa, turn off the light” when it’s time to get some sleep.
[IMPROVE HOME SECURITY] With the BRAUMM App, you are able to check and control your home devices while in bed, at work, or on the go. The timer and countdown functions allow you to turn your decorations and security lights on or off whenever you want.
[SETUP IS A BREEZE] It takes only a few minutes to download and register the BRAUMM App. Adding the plug into the App only takes a few seconds. Alexa and Google Home will automatically discover the plug once the BRAUMM skill is enabled. Also compatible with SmartLife App.
[LIMITED LIFETIME WARRANTY] Join millions of satisfied customers with our limited lifetime warranty, backed by our experienced and dedicated USA based customer service.

product_name: BRAUMM WiFi Smart Plug 2 Packs ETL Listed Smart WiFi Plug Remote Monitor Outlet Timer Compatible with Alexa and Google Assistant Voice Control
product_title: BRAUMM WiFi Smart Plug (2 Packs), ETL Listed Smart WiFi Plug Remote Monitor, Outlet Timer Compatible with Alexa and Google Assistant Voice Control
short_description:
Easy Setup and Safety for You and Your Family.
The WiFi smart plug is ready to pair once it’s plugged in. No additional hub required. Just download the BRAUMM app and follow the in-app instructions to pair the plug(s) with the app. The overcurrent protection cuts off power when the plug is overloaded.
Set Schedule, Smart Scenes and Automation.
Improve home security and use BRAUMM app to create schedules to automate your plug(s) when you are away from home. You can also use Smart Scene to turn on/off a group of devices for special occasions. The Automation will turn on/off the fan or lights based on the weather, temperature, etc.
long_description:
[INSTANTLY UPGRADE TO A SMART OUTLET] The BRAUMM WiFi smart plug can easily upgrade your standard outlet to a multifunctional smart outlet. With the BRAUMM app, you are able to automate the smart outlet any way you like. The plug ONLY supports 2.4G WiFi, and no hub is required.
[VOICE CONTROL] Link your smart plug to Alexa or Google Assistant via the BRAUMM Control Alexa Skill or Google Action. Name your device whatever you want, and enjoy the convenience of Alexa or Google Assistant. Say “Alexa, turn off the light” when it’s time to get some sleep.
[IMPROVE HOME SECURITY] With the BRAUMM App, you are able to check and control your home devices while in bed, at work, or on the go. The timer and countdown functions allow you to turn your decorations and security lights on or off whenever you want.
[SETUP IS A BREEZE] It takes only a few minutes to download and register the BRAUMM App. Adding the plug into the App only takes a few seconds. Alexa and Google Home will automatically discover the plug once the BRAUMM skill is enabled. Also compatible with SmartLife App.
[LIMITED LIFETIME WARRANTY] Join millions of satisfied customers with our limited lifetime warranty, backed by our experienced and dedicated USA based customer service.
